name: Virgin Hair Care
description: This is your one stop shop for everything you need to care for your hair! We co-wash all hair before we ship them out. Want to take it a step further? Get your hair washed, deep conditioned and treated before you get it! This will extend the life of your virgin hair. Also, want to prevent your hair from any bits of shedding? Get your hair weft (tracks) sealed before you receive your hair! This will ensure all of your hair stay the same length and keep its thickness. Want all the recommended products to keep your hair to last up to 2 years? Get your Virgin Hair Care kit! It includes shampoo, conditioner, argon oil, hair spray, and frizz control and second option includes weft sealing.
